# Sign-in allow-list. Copy this to data/allowed_emails.txt and edit.
# One entry per line. Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
# It is read fresh on every sign-in, so changes apply without a restart.
#
# Entry forms:
#   you@example.com     a single exact address
#   *@example.com       any address at that domain
#   *                   anyone (open sign-up — use with care)

you@example.com
*@example.com
